org.gvsig.raster.wms.app.wmsclient.layer

Class ComposedLayerWMS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.fmap.mapcontext.layers.operations.ComposedLayer
      • org.gvsig.raster.wms.app.wmsclient.layer.ComposedLayerWMS

  • public class ComposedLayerWMS
extends ComposedLayer
    Group WMS layers to make a single request to the server for all layers. It is posible only if almost all params are the same. For this comparasion, ComposedLayerWMS uses the method org.gvsig.wms.fmap.layers.FLyrWMS#isComposedLayerCompatible(com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.layers.FLayer)
    See Also:
    com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.layers.layerOperations.ComposedLayer, org.gvsig.wms.fmap.layers.FLyrWMS
